examples.translation: レシピはナツメグを必要とする。

etymology.value: From Middle English notemuge, from Old French note mugue. Equivalent to note +‎ mugge. Compare nutmeg.

usage_notes.explanation: This word is obsolete, meaning it is no longer in general use. It is an archaic form of 'nutmeg'.

readability_explanation.text: This word is obsolete and not commonly encountered in modern English.
